#include<iostream>
#include<map>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    map <string,string> mp;
    int n,q;
    string a1,a2,x;
    cin >> n >> q;
    while(n--)
    {
        cin >> a1 >> a2;
        mp[a2] = a1;
    }
    map <string , string> :: iterator it;
    while(q--)
    {
        cin >> x;
        it = mp.find(x);
        if(!(it == mp.end()))
            cout << it->second << endl;
        else
            cout << "Name not found" << endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
